#: ../../docs/training_manual/basic_map/overview.rst:165
msgid ""
"Now that you are familiar with the basics of the QGIS interface, in the next"
" lesson we will see how to load some common data types."
msgstr ""
"Sada kada ste upoznati sa osnovama QGIS interfejsa, u sledećoj lekciji "
"videćemo kako da učitamo neke uobičajene tipove podataka."
